PERMISSIONS AND RESTRICTIONS

✅ PERMITTED (You may):

- Use AEGIS internally for your business
- Modify the source code for your own purposes
- Run self-hosted instances
- Contribute improvements back to the project
- Use AEGIS in applications you build for customers
- Deploy on your own infrastructure

❌ PROHIBITED (You may not):

- Offer AEGIS as a managed SaaS service to third parties
- Resell or rebrand AEGIS as your own managed offering
- Provide AEGIS as a cloud service without explicit commercial license

For cloud provider partnerships or managed service arrangements, please
contact <licensing@100monkeys.ai>

